---
// src/components/AboutSection.astro
---

<section id="about" class="relative py-20 overflow-hidden scroll-mt-24">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10">
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50/30 via-transparent to-purple-50/30 dark:from-blue-900/10 dark:via-transparent dark:to-purple-900/10"
    >
    </div>
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full opacity-40">
      <svg
        class="w-full h-full"
        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
        viewBox="0 0 1440 320"
      >
        <path
          fill="currentColor"
          class="text-blue-200/20 dark:text-blue-800/20"
          fill-opacity="1"
          d="M0,96L48,112C96,128,192,160,288,160C384,160,480,128,576,122.7C672,117,768,139,864,138.7C960,139,1056,117,1152,106.7C1248,96,1344,96,1392,96L1440,96L1440,320L1392,320C1344,320,1248,320,1152,320C1056,320,960,320,864,320C768,320,672,320,576,320C480,320,384,320,288,320C192,320,96,320,48,320L0,320Z"
        ></path>
      </svg>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container max-w-4xl px-6 mx-auto">
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-12">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-6 text-center">
        <h2
          class="relative inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-3 text-3xl font-bold md:text-4xl text-slate-900 dark:text-white font-display"
        >
          <!-- Icono Usuario Check -->
          <svg
            class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400"
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            width="24"
            height="24"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke="currentColor"
            fill="none"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            ><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"></path><path
              d="M8 7a4 4 0 1 0 8 0a4 4 0 0 0 -8 0"></path><path
              d="M6 21v-2a4 4 0 0 1 4 -4h4"></path><path d="M15 19l2 2l4 -4"
            ></path></svg
          >
          Acerca de mí
          <span
            class="absolute bottom-0 w-24 h-1 transform -translate-x-1/2 rounded-full left-1/2 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-purple-500"
          ></span>
        </h2>
        <p
          class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300"
        >
          Desarrollador web de Camagüey, Cuba, graduado en la Universidad
          Ignacio Agramonte Loynaz, especializado en crear experiencias
          digitales únicas.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid items-center gap-12 md:grid-cols-2">
        <div class="flex flex-col order-2 gap-8 md:order-1">
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <h3
              class="flex items-center gap-2 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 font-display"
            >
              <!-- Icono Código -->
              <svg
                class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                width="24"
                height="24"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                stroke-width="2"
                stroke="currentColor"
                fill="none"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                ><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"></path><path
                  d="M7 8l-4 4l4 4"></path><path d="M17 8l4 4l-4 4"></path><path
                  d="M14 4l-4 16"></path></svg
              >
              Sobre mí
            </h3>
            <p class="leading-relaxed text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">
              Soy un desarrollador web de Camagüey, Cuba. Apasionado por la
              tecnología y la innovación, me especializo en crear soluciones
              digitales modernas y eficientes que ayuden a las empresas a crecer
              en el mundo digital.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <h3
              class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 font-display"
            >
              Educación
            </h3>
            <p class="leading-relaxed text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">
              Graduado en Ingeniería Informática en la Universidad Ignacio
              Agramonte Loynaz de Camagüey, con especialización en desarrollo
              web y tecnologías modernas. Constantemente actualizando mis
              conocimientos para ofrecer las mejores soluciones.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <h3
              class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 font-display"
            >
              Experiencia
            </h3>
            <p class="leading-relaxed text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">
              He trabajado en diversos proyectos de desarrollo web, tanto en
              Cuba como internacionalmente, creando aplicaciones web modernas y
              responsivas que se adaptan a las necesidades de cada cliente.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex justify-center order-1 md:order-2">
          <div class="relative group">
            <div
              class="absolute transition duration-1000 opacity-25 -inset-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-purple-600 rounded-3xl blur group-hover:opacity-40"
            >
            </div>
            <div
              class="relative overflow-hidden transition-all duration-500 transform border-4 border-white shadow-2xl rounded-3xl dark:border-slate-800 -rotate-3 group-hover:-rotate-1 group-hover:scale-105"
            >
              <img
                src="/images/sobre.webp"
                alt="Foto de Reineldi Umpierre"
                class="object-cover transition-transform duration-700 w-80 h-80 group-hover:scale-110"
                width="320"
                height="320"
                loading="lazy"
              />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  @keyframes fadeInLeft {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateX(-30px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateX(0);
    }
  }
  @keyframes fadeInRight {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateX(30px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateX(0);
    }
  }
  .md\:grid > div:first-child {
    animation: fadeInLeft 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1) forwards;
    opacity: 0;
  }
  .md\:grid > div:last-child {
    animation: fadeInRight 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1) forwards;
    opacity: 0;
  }
</style>
